title: Value Index of Imports for Consumption for United States
notes:
These Data Are For General Imports Through 1933 And For Consumption From 1934-1953. Source: Survey Of Current Business July, 1951, Pp. 27-28 For 1929-1949 Data; Quarterly Summary Of Foreign Commerce For 1950-1952. 1953 Data Are From Survey Of Current Business.

This NBER data series m07051 appears on the NBER website in Chapter 7 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter07.html.
